---
By: Annamalai Swami
Locus:
  Page: 432
  Verse: 6
Tags:
  - Simplicity
---
Our purpose in life is to realize the Self.It is an easy matter to get a
little foodand find somewhere congenial to liveand meditate. Once we have
achievedthis we should have no further interestin the world and its
problems.
